{{vgname|永不孤单|en=Never Alone|ik=Kisima Inŋitchuŋa}}是Upper One Games推出的[[平台游戏|平台游戏]]。在这款游戏中，玩家可以操作主角[[因纽特人|因纽特人]]Nuna和她的[[北极狐|北极狐]]同伴，解决谜题，完成以阿拉斯加原住民故事为蓝本的八个关卡。这款游戏是[[库克湾|库克湾]]部落理事会与 E-Line Media 协作的产物，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/sep/29/never-alone-alaskas-indigenous-game-never-alone-teaches-cooperation-through-stories|title=Alaska's indigenous game Never Alone teaches co-operation through stories|first=Hannah Jane|last=Parkinson|date=September 29, 2014|newspaper=The Guardian|access-date=July 1, 2016|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216174622/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/sep/29/never-alone-alaskas-indigenous-game-never-alone-teaches-cooperation-through-stories|dead-url=no}}</ref>是日渐增多的[[原住民|原住民]]团体开发的[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]之一。

